title: Troy & Michael Discover... | American Horror Stories - Episode 2: "Rubber (Wo)man - Part Two" (HD)
author: AHS Crave
comment: All of those young, aspiring actresses out there and the role was given to a model that can't act? Absolutely ridiculous. And it's to the detriment of the show! That's what I don't understand - don't they want their show to be the best it can be?
description:
Ruby (Kaia Gerber) watches as Scarlett's dads (Matt Bomer & Gavin Creel) discover the truth about their current existence.
